{
  "stem": "3952.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was like 2:00, 3:00 in the morning when they arrived from the train, and we brought them home to some relative.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I helped bringing in the valises, their-- their baggages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my oldest sister said-- said to one of the other sisters, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Give something to the [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I helped them bring in the baggage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And only when I smiled, she recognized me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Oh, this is Icu.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She didn't know that-- she didn't recognize me, because I was suddenly round in the face, so blown up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Another little curiosity of what eating can do to you and not eating can do to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, after six months, we decided we will go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And going to Israel means that you walk all the borders, the Romania-Hungarian border, the whole night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The Hungarian-- Austria border-- Austrian border, the whole night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then Austria was divided in three zones-- the British, English-- British, American, and French zone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you cross-- each one has a border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to cross by night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got to the American zone, where we heard that there is an organization of Aliyah Bet that will take us to Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in a camp called Admont, which is close to a city called Graz, not far away from Klagenfurt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there for six months, doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I mean, all-- most of the people were doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working in the-- in the store where we provided the food for the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since I spoke English, they needed translation, so they took me to the office to translate when they needed that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew German and I knew English, and they caught SS people running away, or SS people who were hiding, like, DP persons.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
